  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  The failure of healing after at least 16 weeks and not more than 9 months following
             surgical reduction and fixation of the fracture.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Implant loosening or failure, infection, established nonunion, fracture gap greater
             than 5 mm, presence of implant within the fracture gap, metabolic disorders or
             received medication affecting fracture healing
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
